faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707786bb0fb50c077d8204bf7e56b5aef342dc98","tid":174074,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T14:42:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有朋友收養埋左一堆貓仔 因為太多貓 搞唔掂</span></span><br />\n<br />\n言下之意即係棄養？<br />\n定係佢只係做暫托 你講清楚啲好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37f865a5a8ca1d7228f77cda54c3251cf57d87c","tid":174074,"uid":60953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T14:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有朋友收養埋左一堆貓仔 因為太多貓 搞唔掂</span></span><br />\n<br />\n言下之意即係棄養？<br />\n定係佢只係做暫托 你講清楚啲好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔會幫棄養既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5194a7e897c87dd863c1de19b7ebdd970ad9a52","tid":174074,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T14:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有朋友收養埋左一堆貓仔 因為太多貓 搞唔掂</span></span><br />\n<br />\n言下之意即係棄養？<br />\n定係佢只係做暫托 你講清楚啲好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔會幫棄養既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咩唔帶佢地去打針？ 連第一針都唔打<br />\n打針，杜蟲，滴頸做咗先喇 有人要咪收返針錢"},{"pid":"7cc1235d3cd436a3c5199cc52f62aa4bf574a9d8","tid":174074,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有朋友收養埋左一堆貓仔 因為太多貓 搞唔掂</span></span><br />\n<br />\n言下之意即係棄養？<br />\n定係佢只係做暫托 你講清楚啲好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔會幫棄養既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咩唔帶佢地去打針？ 連第一針都唔打<br />\n打針，杜蟲，滴頸做咗先喇 有人要咪收返針錢</blockquote><br />\n幫貓仔搵領養都比人批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能佢冇時間或者冇咁多錢幫所有貓仔打針姐<br />\n真係錫貓仔既話領養左之後自然會帶佢去睇醫生打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6b86f70cc9b7bb9163b2318e3b76972e37404d","tid":174074,"uid":60953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有朋友收養埋左一堆貓仔 因為太多貓 搞唔掂</span></span><br />\n<br />\n言下之意即係棄養？<br />\n定係佢只係做暫托 你講清楚啲好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔會幫棄養既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咩唔帶佢地去打針？ 連第一針都唔打<br />\n打針，杜蟲，滴頸做咗先喇 有人要咪收返針錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都問緊 不過都係想幫貓仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ead8e74dc0d7e0ecc4043abcc833e23a880084","tid":174074,"uid":2860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T15:02:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f62e1c67cb802e1e12d403f68183775a228d501","tid":174074,"uid":57494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T15:12:17.000Z","msg":"幫推，希望快啲可以搵到好主人"},{"pid":"a8c53d9cffcf0c89147a280f76ff6091127788d7","tid":174074,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T15:21:03.000Z","msg":"想養 但未養過貓 可唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf13207500cb4259daf5f37bcf4f25350675cfd","tid":174074,"uid":63350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T15:21:50.000Z","msg":"棄養死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30893104bbfc794857949769ffe81f5be4734f1c","tid":174074,"uid":60953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"